    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomatoes</strong> finely</p>",
