    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>diced chicken thigh </strong>to the pan and cook for an initial 5 min</p><p>Combine your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> with 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml] </span>[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
