      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 5 min, add the <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>ras el hanout </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato stock </strong>and cook, covered, for a further 6-8 min, or until the sweet potatoes are tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
