    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong> with a small splash of <strong>boiled water</strong> until it's loosened to a paste</p><p>Add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and grind (or chop if you don't have a pestle and mortar) to a fine powder</p>",
      "order": 6,
