    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add the <strong>peanut butter</strong> and<strong> half </strong>the<strong> ground almonds</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(save the rest for later!)<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to the pan and stir thoroughly for 1 min or until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Remove from the heat and stir through <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) – this is your <strong>maffe-style chicken stew</strong></p>",
