      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>maffe-style chicken stew</strong> over the <strong>brown rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>ground almonds</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
